Class FcmApns.Builder

java.lang.Object
io.github.waileong.fcm.service.domain.FcmApns.Builder
Enclosing class:
FcmApns
public static final class FcmApns.Builder extends Object
Builder class for FcmApns. Provides a fluent interface for constructing an FcmApns instance with specified headers, payload, and options.
